Harm reduction advices and tips for safer partying. Since 2013 the people presenting psy help delivers harm reduction services to goa/ psytrance parties and festivals.

Sara Niksic a.k.a. Inner Child is a marine biologist, musician and combinations of these. During the lecture you will hear about Sara’s research into whale song culture, underwater bioacoustics and ocean conservation and the story behind her two albums: Song of the Humpback Whale and The Evolution.
During his research, Ovidiu has identified at least 20 types of awakening journeys and their specific challenges; you will discuss them and explore how to invite an awakening intentionally.

NVC’s target is to improve the quality of our life and so it can help to develop empathy, repair connections, enhance self-counciousness, personal growth and decrease conflicts. The workshop will consist of a short theory then practical excercises.
